{"tid":851870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊匪潤雄：母語請你回家學","createTime":"2018-10-07T12:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T16:50:51.000Z","uid":202262,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b82157eb156a33002e4914d7ea4289b7ad137a","tid":851870,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:48:24.000Z","msg":"早幾日台灣嘅中國國民黨高雄市長參選人韓國瑜 就話：母語請你回家學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5VpmbRt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VpmbRt.jpg&h=cd020eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日香港 楊匪潤雄：世界學中文，你想下有哪些地方（學）廣東話？其實無的&hellip;&hellip;即是說成個世界將來的中文發展，是以普通話為主。香港700萬人社會用廣東話學中文，將來會不會長遠？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xZsfgh9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZsfgh9.jpg&h=1aea3360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果將佢改一改就變：世界學中文，你想下有哪些地方（學）台語？其實無的&hellip;&hellip;即是說成個世界將來的中文發展，是以普通話為主。台灣2300萬人社會用台語學中文，將來會不會長遠？<br />\n<br />\n係咪好無違和感呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec558598182ae3f106e827ddd608d6c12c11ebe","tid":851870,"uid":45332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:49:57.000Z","msg":"dklm"},{"pid":"8bbef0c9a3466944dc6978eb2ac535942b16899b","tid":851870,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:50:35.000Z","msg":"死全家"},{"pid":"d9e536eb220db4ade651d397d382532759e36f5a","tid":851870,"uid":66242,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:51:41.000Z","msg":"全世界除咗日本，有無國家係以日語為母語呢？"},{"pid":"e067dc9cf71a4ef074abbcc3696c96a1b7466eae","tid":851870,"uid":66242,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:52:29.000Z","msg":"全世界除咗泰國，有無國家係以泰語為母語呢？"},{"pid":"1c1b4471135b5a83d37a23bb015fd841663693ad","tid":851870,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:53:58.000Z","msg":"有冇人留